'''赫尔穆特·克雷默斯'''（{{lang-de|'''Helmut Kremers'''}}，{{bd|1949年|3月24日|catIdx=Kremers, Helmut}}），前[[德国|德国]][[足球|足球]][[运动员|运动员]]，场上司职[[後衛_(足球)|后卫]]。他与其孪生兄弟[[埃尔文·克雷默斯|埃尔文·克雷默斯]]均曾入选过[[西德国家足球队|西德国家足球队]]，并随队夺得[[1974年世界杯|1974年世界杯]]冠军，两人也是[[德甲|德甲]]历史上出现的首对[[双胞胎|双胞胎]]球员<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2007/oct/10/theknowledge.sport | title = Who has scored the most hat-tricks in a single season? | date = 2007-10-10 | author = James Dart and Paolo Bandini | publisher = guardian.co.uk | accessdate = 2011-09-09 | archive-date = 2008-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080812074049/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2007/oct/10/theknowledge.sport | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

